<ab facs="#facs_110_r1l1"><expan>ſchaff<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ er ſıch des . Oder <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> recht / dıe vormals <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Steͣtem = </ab>
